WEBVTT

00:15.460 --> 00:19.960
笙ｪDuring the dark night笙ｪ

00:20.100 --> 00:22.750
笙ｪA guiding light笙ｪ

00:23.260 --> 00:25.050
笙ｪJust like you笙ｪ

00:25.460 --> 00:29.750
笙ｪMakes life turn bright笙ｪ

00:30.330 --> 00:35.180
笙ｪBreaking free from darkness笙ｪ

00:35.400 --> 00:38.880
笙ｪYou gave me strength笙ｪ

00:39.230 --> 00:41.780
笙ｪRunning for truth笙ｪ

00:41.800 --> 00:45.850
笙ｪI find my path笙ｪ

00:46.600 --> 00:50.580
笙ｪDrawing on the hope笙ｪ

00:51.200 --> 00:54.580
笙ｪThat you render me笙ｪ

00:55.130 --> 00:58.010
笙ｪIn this long journey笙ｪ

00:58.260 --> 01:01.680
笙ｪI run on lightly笙ｪ

01:19.180 --> 01:22.980
[Reborn]
[Adapted from Qiang Yu's work, Reborn]

01:26.050 --> 01:27.180
[Class 5 Grade 3, Senior High]

01:33.780 --> 01:37.220
[Make your dreams come true.]

01:37.220 --> 01:39.460
Hard work and persistence

01:39.490 --> 01:41.490
will change your life
and help you achieve your dreams.

01:41.810 --> 01:44.650
Everyone, the NCEE isn't the end,

01:45.140 --> 01:46.170
[Let your grit shine.]
but your first step

01:46.170 --> 01:47.620
[Make your dreams come true.]
into adulthood.

01:48.050 --> 01:50.330
Thus, the coming year
is of great importance.

01:50.620 --> 01:51.740
I hope you all work hard,

01:52.050 --> 01:54.330
and push yourselves even further.

01:54.490 --> 01:57.370
Only by giving it your all
will you make the most of your youth.

01:57.620 --> 02:01.220
- Give it my all with no regrets!
- Give it my all with no regrets!

02:02.500 --> 02:03.090
Good.

02:03.180 --> 02:04.540
Now, let's look at our textbook.

02:04.540 --> 02:07.050
We'll start the first lesson
of the third year of high school.

02:07.220 --> 02:08.220
Before we get started,

02:08.220 --> 02:10.330
let's go over the plan for the year.

02:14.690 --> 02:16.130
Qingyu, what was your answer

02:16.130 --> 02:18.090
to the last multiple-choice question?

02:18.300 --> 02:19.730
I chose A and C.

02:20.260 --> 02:21.540
I don't remember.

02:23.130 --> 02:25.090
What about the last question
for Comprehensive Science?

02:25.090 --> 02:26.010
Did you get it?

02:26.300 --> 02:27.050
Yes, I did.

02:27.050 --> 02:28.380
Can you explain it to me?

02:28.460 --> 02:28.570
Okay.

02:28.570 --> 02:29.980
I just can't figure it out.

02:29.980 --> 02:30.460
Sure.

02:30.460 --> 02:33.210
Can we not talk about the exams
during lunch break?

02:33.490 --> 02:34.180
It's annoying.

02:34.180 --> 02:35.130
Ignore her, Qingyu.

02:35.130 --> 02:37.329
Exactly. Keep work and life balanced.

02:37.329 --> 02:38.460
Just take a break.

02:38.460 --> 02:39.290
Qiao Qingyu!

02:39.620 --> 02:41.290
Go see Mr. Sun in his office.

02:46.490 --> 02:47.410
Mr. Sun.

02:47.690 --> 02:49.380
Oh, Qingyu.

02:49.490 --> 02:50.410
You asked for me?

02:50.740 --> 02:51.210
Yeah.

02:51.690 --> 02:52.690
Your dad called.

02:56.050 --> 02:56.850
Hello?

02:57.050 --> 02:57.900
Qing?

02:58.260 --> 02:59.050
Um...

03:00.050 --> 03:01.050
I'm

03:01.490 --> 03:02.980
on my way back to Nanqiao Village.

03:03.570 --> 03:04.690
Your grandpa passed away.

03:05.570 --> 03:07.540
Qing, are you listening?

03:07.820 --> 03:08.380
Yes.

03:09.570 --> 03:11.290
I left the key to the drawer at home

03:11.290 --> 03:12.330
with Qiao Huan.

03:12.330 --> 03:13.740
Grab the passbook when you get home.

03:13.740 --> 03:14.770
Get Yu tonight

03:14.770 --> 03:16.690
to come back
to Nanqiao Village together.

03:37.230 --> 03:40.000
[Passbook]

03:52.400 --> 03:57.300
[Episode 20]
[Fanghao Unleashed]

04:11.500 --> 04:13.540
Dad and Mom had told

04:13.850 --> 04:17.060
Grandma and Grandpa
about Qiao Beiyu's funeral.

04:19.610 --> 04:23.130
I remember
it was the Chinese New Year's Eve.

04:23.570 --> 04:24.690
It was still dark outside

04:24.820 --> 04:27.010
when we got to Shunyun Funeral Parlor.

04:27.730 --> 04:31.660
We waited for a long time,
but no one showed up.

04:32.540 --> 04:33.940
We had to book the farewell hall

04:33.940 --> 04:35.980
at the funeral parlor in advance.

04:37.690 --> 04:39.940
But we missed the timing
because we waited

04:40.260 --> 04:41.500
for Grandpa and Grandma.

04:41.780 --> 04:47.010
In the end, Qiao Beiyu was cremated

04:47.010 --> 04:48.940
without a proper wake.

04:51.940 --> 04:55.060
Do you think at the time,
our grandparents

04:55.820 --> 04:58.060
and uncles

04:58.260 --> 05:00.220
were seated around a table

05:00.340 --> 05:02.890
for the reunion dinner as usual?

05:15.130 --> 05:17.780
I guess it was a good thing
they didn't show up.

05:19.260 --> 05:21.610
It saved her from one last scolding.

05:35.540 --> 05:35.980
Six...

05:36.130 --> 05:37.980
Ah, I'm drawing a tile.

05:38.170 --> 05:39.100
Here it is.

05:39.930 --> 05:40.540
Wow.

05:41.050 --> 05:41.490
Listen,

05:41.490 --> 05:42.460
I'm going to win

05:42.460 --> 05:43.610
with how the game is going today.

05:43.980 --> 05:45.580
Is that so? Don't be so sure.

05:45.730 --> 05:47.140
You never know.

05:47.140 --> 05:48.780
I have a feeling

05:48.930 --> 05:51.290
that my luck is better
than Yanfen's today.

05:51.659 --> 05:52.980
Let's see who's more lucky.

05:52.980 --> 05:54.250
It's not down to luck.

05:54.250 --> 05:55.460
Today, when I left home,

05:55.460 --> 05:57.020
a bird was chirping above me.

06:13.930 --> 06:14.780
Yu, Qing.

06:14.780 --> 06:15.410
Come in. Quick.

06:15.410 --> 06:16.370
Let me take your things.

06:16.580 --> 06:18.700
Go and pay respect to Grandpa.

06:18.700 --> 06:19.410
Go on.

06:20.610 --> 06:21.540
Hurry up.

06:22.900 --> 06:23.410
Dad.

06:25.980 --> 06:27.220
Here you are.

06:37.020 --> 06:37.810
Go ahead.

06:38.780 --> 06:39.409
Here.

07:01.660 --> 07:02.540
Yu.

07:03.810 --> 07:05.900
You are now the Qiaos' eldest grandson.

07:06.660 --> 07:07.460
You have a great responsibility.

07:07.730 --> 07:09.250
From tonight to dawn tomorrow,

07:09.290 --> 07:11.580
you'll have to keep watch
over Grandpa's wake.

07:11.580 --> 07:12.610
During the funeral procession tomorrow,

07:12.610 --> 07:14.410
you'll follow behind Uncle Haisheng,

07:14.490 --> 07:15.850
carrying Grandpa's portrait.

07:15.850 --> 07:16.660
Got that?

07:17.140 --> 07:17.490
Hmm.

07:17.490 --> 07:19.250
All right, keep that in mind.

07:19.250 --> 07:19.930
One character tile.

07:23.900 --> 07:24.700
Self-drawn.

07:24.930 --> 07:26.930
My goodness, your luck is incredible!

07:29.020 --> 07:30.850
Told you.

07:36.170 --> 07:36.780
Here.

07:36.780 --> 07:37.780
Here you go.

07:39.140 --> 07:39.930
South Wind.

07:40.050 --> 07:41.050
You're going to lose the Wind.

07:41.050 --> 07:41.810
Go ahead with the South.

07:57.810 --> 07:58.930
Here.

08:03.100 --> 08:04.020
Drink up.

08:04.980 --> 08:05.810
Help yourself.

08:06.900 --> 08:07.610
Come on.

08:08.850 --> 08:09.370
Thanks.

08:10.810 --> 08:11.490
Fanghao.

08:11.810 --> 08:12.220
Yes?

08:12.220 --> 08:13.050
Get us some hot water.

08:13.050 --> 08:13.610
Okay.

08:15.100 --> 08:17.660
We're hungry. Make some noodles for us.

08:18.220 --> 08:20.580
Oh, I have to check on Mom later.

08:20.580 --> 08:21.700
I'll cook for you after that.

08:21.980 --> 08:22.730
Fanghao,

08:22.780 --> 08:24.250
your family has been running
the noodle shop for a long time.

08:24.250 --> 08:26.410
I've been wanting to try your cooking.

08:27.220 --> 08:28.930
What would you like? Feel free to order.

08:29.250 --> 08:30.540
Never mind. It's too much hassle.

08:30.540 --> 08:31.850
There's plenty of alcohol today.

08:31.850 --> 08:34.409
Let's keep it lively
in such an occasion.

08:35.580 --> 08:36.980
Fanghao.

08:37.370 --> 08:39.140
Coming.

08:39.140 --> 08:40.659
Fanghao.

08:41.220 --> 08:42.220
I'm coming, Mom.

08:42.220 --> 08:43.730
Fanghao...

08:43.730 --> 08:44.730
It's too bothersome.

08:47.290 --> 08:50.340
We just asked her a small favor,
and look how annoyed she is.

08:50.340 --> 08:51.700
What is her problem?

08:51.900 --> 08:54.370
Yanfen, Jinrui's grandfather
had been sick for a long time.

08:54.370 --> 08:55.850
She had to take care of everything.

08:55.850 --> 08:57.370
Give her a break, won't you?

08:57.370 --> 08:58.490
No one forced her.

08:58.490 --> 08:59.460
She did it willingly.

08:59.460 --> 09:01.140
Exactly. Every family has its elders.

09:01.140 --> 09:02.340
It is indeed exhausting.

09:02.810 --> 09:04.370
Okay, let's keep playing.

09:04.490 --> 09:05.290
Whose turn is it?

09:05.930 --> 09:06.850
It's my turn.

09:18.700 --> 09:19.490
Mom.

09:20.140 --> 09:21.170
Why are you still up?

09:22.290 --> 09:23.850
The noise kept me awake.

09:26.850 --> 09:27.490
I thought

09:27.490 --> 09:29.140
you were coming back
to take care of Grandma.

09:29.140 --> 09:31.290
Why are you doing
everything around the house?

09:31.340 --> 09:33.100
There's

09:33.780 --> 09:35.490
no difference.

09:35.900 --> 09:37.020
Nothing to complain about.

09:37.540 --> 09:38.810
They're taking advantage of you

09:38.810 --> 09:39.980
and you're just letting it happen.

09:42.050 --> 09:43.730
I've long come to my senses.

09:44.460 --> 09:45.850
People live

09:46.050 --> 09:47.460
to suffer.

09:48.290 --> 09:51.780
You can't run from the inevitable,
so you just endure it.

09:52.250 --> 09:54.980
When the time comes
for you to leave the world,

09:55.700 --> 09:56.850
you'll be free.

10:00.130 --> 10:01.700
Your sister was freed.

10:02.250 --> 10:03.890
And now your grandpa is too.

10:33.530 --> 10:34.610
How is Mom?

10:35.580 --> 10:36.700
She just fell asleep.

10:37.300 --> 10:38.530
She's not eating much though.

10:39.610 --> 10:42.460
Gosh, people always talk about
the importance of elderly companionship.

10:42.460 --> 10:44.730
Now Dad is gone and Mom is left alone.

10:45.130 --> 10:47.610
How will she live her days now?

10:51.820 --> 10:53.340
Well, Fanghao,

10:53.340 --> 10:54.820
why don't you sit down
and rest for a bit?

10:55.650 --> 10:56.530
I'm good.

11:01.180 --> 11:03.010
You've done so much.

11:05.250 --> 11:08.610
Haisheng, just be frank.

11:10.940 --> 11:14.580
Now that everyone's here,

11:15.010 --> 11:17.940
I want to discuss Mom's future care.

11:18.340 --> 11:19.530
Since Dad passed,

11:20.180 --> 11:22.490
she's been bedridden
after suffering a shock.

11:23.490 --> 11:24.850
What should we do now?

11:26.980 --> 11:27.580
Oh.

11:28.940 --> 11:29.940
Here, Haisheng.

11:30.300 --> 11:32.820
Here are Mom's living expenses
for the next six months.

11:35.850 --> 11:37.850
It's not about the money.

11:39.420 --> 11:40.370
More importantly,

11:40.370 --> 11:42.300
your wife has been looking after Mom
for a long time.

11:42.700 --> 11:45.890
We're worried changing caretakers
will upset her routine.

11:46.180 --> 11:48.940
Okay. Qingyu is sitting
for the NCEE next year.

11:49.490 --> 11:51.820
I can come back after
and take care of Mom.

11:51.890 --> 11:53.130
Since you two are busy,

11:53.850 --> 11:55.890
we'll look after Mom for now.

11:56.890 --> 11:58.460
But make sure you give us
the monthly allowance.

11:59.100 --> 12:02.010
Anyway, we'd be taking care
of her final days.

12:02.650 --> 12:03.890
Also,

12:04.180 --> 12:05.370
before he died,

12:05.650 --> 12:08.250
Dad said he wanted Jinrui
to have this house.

12:08.610 --> 12:09.890
You guys are fine with that, right?

12:11.820 --> 12:12.730
Fine with me.

12:16.490 --> 12:17.180
Okay.

12:18.300 --> 12:19.300
There's one more thing.

12:19.730 --> 12:22.580
People are saying that our family
has met with constant misfortune

12:22.610 --> 12:24.580
because something went wrong
with the ancestral grave.

12:26.890 --> 12:28.010
What's wrong?

12:28.770 --> 12:30.700
It's because of Qiao Beiyu.

12:40.700 --> 12:42.220
Let's

12:42.300 --> 12:43.300
set a date

12:43.820 --> 12:45.180
to move Bei's ashes

12:45.730 --> 12:47.130
from the ancestral grave.

12:49.730 --> 12:50.650
Move her?

12:50.650 --> 12:51.980
Where can she go?

12:52.490 --> 12:55.890
Just so you know,
relocating her is a necessity.

12:56.060 --> 12:57.940
She should blame herself
for messing things up

12:57.940 --> 12:59.220
since such a young age.

12:59.340 --> 13:01.650
If you had asked me, she shouldn't have
been buried at the ancestral grave.

13:01.650 --> 13:02.490
Look for a lake or river to...

13:02.490 --> 13:03.010
Chen Yanfen.

13:04.460 --> 13:05.220
Say it again. I dare you.

13:05.220 --> 13:06.100
So what?

13:06.100 --> 13:06.940
She is a jinx!

13:06.940 --> 13:07.490
Say that again.

13:07.490 --> 13:08.580
She is dead and yet she's...

13:09.060 --> 13:10.010
What are you doing?

13:10.010 --> 13:10.820
Don't get physical!

13:11.010 --> 13:12.340
Mom! Mom!

13:12.490 --> 13:13.300
What are you doing?

13:13.490 --> 13:14.250
What are you doing?

13:14.250 --> 13:15.700
Lusheng, stop your wife!

13:15.890 --> 13:16.940
Are you mad?

13:30.010 --> 13:30.650
Get over here!

13:31.010 --> 13:31.850
Stop fighting!

13:31.980 --> 13:34.010
Mom! Mom!

13:34.460 --> 13:37.340
Mom! Qiao Beiyu hated Nanqiao Village!

13:37.980 --> 13:39.100
Forget about the genealogy book
and ancestral grave!

13:39.100 --> 13:40.130
We don't need any of them!

13:40.130 --> 13:41.250
We'll take Beiyu away.

13:56.820 --> 13:57.610
Fine.

13:59.820 --> 14:00.610
We'll relocate the grave.

16:48.900 --> 16:50.530
[To Qiao's Handmade Noodle House]

16:54.180 --> 16:55.370
Dad, Mom.

16:55.770 --> 16:57.420
I know you've worked tirelessly

16:57.420 --> 16:59.180
to raise our family.

16:59.650 --> 17:00.730
When I grow up,

17:00.730 --> 17:02.010
I will find a good job

17:02.250 --> 17:04.460
so that you two can live a happy life.

17:04.730 --> 17:06.940
I don't want you two
to have to work so hard.

17:08.060 --> 17:09.420
I miss you.

17:23.730 --> 17:27.930
[To Qiao's Handmade Noodle House]

17:30.700 --> 17:34.250
[To Qiao's Handmade Noodle House]

17:49.580 --> 17:50.440
[Happy birthday]
Some say,

17:50.440 --> 17:52.530
[To our beloved daughter Qiao Beiyu]
if life could be exchanged,

17:53.370 --> 17:56.180
heaven would be filled with parents.

17:58.490 --> 18:01.940
Our parents, through their own ways,

18:02.300 --> 18:04.060
both clumsy and stubborn,

18:04.180 --> 18:06.370
have always protected us
no matter what happens.

18:07.100 --> 18:10.100
Their love is silent but profound.

18:10.730 --> 18:12.980
Sometimes it feels overwhelming,

18:13.610 --> 18:17.010
yet it's the same love
that gives us the strength

18:17.250 --> 18:19.420
to overcome the challenges
of growing up.

18:21.130 --> 18:22.460
[Tomb of Our Beloved Daughter]
I desperately longed

18:22.460 --> 18:23.980
[Qiao Beiyu]
to escape this family,

18:24.770 --> 18:27.380
but that feeling is gone now.

18:46.770 --> 18:48.860
This east-facing spot

18:49.220 --> 18:51.380
has fresh air, and a beautiful view.

18:51.620 --> 18:53.420
Qiao Beiyu would love it here.

18:58.220 --> 19:00.050
Hi

19:00.810 --> 19:02.700
everyone,

19:02.810 --> 19:04.660
this is my sister. She's new here.

19:05.330 --> 19:07.490
You all will be neighbors.

19:07.620 --> 19:09.460
Please take care of her.

19:10.140 --> 19:11.010
Please.

19:11.010 --> 19:11.730
Come help out.

19:11.730 --> 19:12.380
Please...

19:41.860 --> 19:42.770
Beiyu.

19:44.380 --> 19:45.940
This place is nice, isn't it?

19:47.810 --> 19:49.490
Your dad and I have thought it through.

19:50.810 --> 19:52.810
Your siblings are right.

19:54.420 --> 19:58.660
Home is wherever we are.

20:02.420 --> 20:04.180
This place is close to Huanzhou.

20:05.570 --> 20:06.530
That means

20:08.090 --> 20:10.290
we'll be able to visit you often.

20:16.140 --> 20:18.220
Beiyu, if you need anything,

20:18.220 --> 20:19.570
you can tell us in our dreams.

20:22.420 --> 20:24.380
No, I'm too chicken.

20:24.380 --> 20:26.010
Don't come into my dreams.

20:26.010 --> 20:27.330
Go tell Qingyu instead.

20:32.810 --> 20:36.010
To be honest, for the past few days,

20:37.010 --> 20:39.220
I kept thinking about our childhood.

20:40.460 --> 20:42.140
If I could go back,

20:44.290 --> 20:47.460
wouldn't it be nice to take another look

20:48.460 --> 20:49.660
at Qiao Beiyu then?

21:50.660 --> 21:51.570
Qiao Beiyu.

21:55.900 --> 21:56.730
Qiao Beiyu!

22:09.010 --> 22:11.140
When you escaped Nanqiao Village
for Shunyun,

22:12.290 --> 22:13.490
you were wearing very little.

22:15.330 --> 22:16.290
Weren't you cold?

22:18.180 --> 22:19.660
Jinrui let you down.

22:19.980 --> 22:21.570
Uncle Haisheng and Aunt Yanfen
blamed you.

22:22.730 --> 22:24.420
You must feel so angry.

22:27.530 --> 22:29.380
You found out you were sick

22:30.090 --> 22:31.730
and went to the hospital alone.

22:33.900 --> 22:35.660
You must have been so scared.

22:40.420 --> 22:41.700
I'm sorry, Qiao Beiyu.

22:43.250 --> 22:45.290
I wish I could be by your side too.

23:05.860 --> 23:07.290
I miss you, Beiyu.

23:33.280 --> 23:36.780
[Half a year later]

23:54.980 --> 23:56.950
[Huanzhou Detention Center]

23:58.420 --> 23:59.420
Welcome back, Hei!

24:24.530 --> 24:25.880
[Qiao Qingyu]

24:33.080 --> 24:35.330
[To Qiao Qingyu]

24:37.620 --> 24:39.730
Qingyu, I hope all's well with you.

24:40.660 --> 24:42.330
When you're reading this letter,

24:42.620 --> 24:44.730
I suppose the new term has started.

24:45.460 --> 24:47.860
Life in university has been
more hectic than I expected.

24:48.010 --> 24:49.530
Nevertheless, it's very fulfilling.

24:49.530 --> 24:52.750
[Yanbei University, Beining]

24:52.750 --> 24:56.580
笙ｪBirds take a fly笙ｪ

24:56.580 --> 25:01.200
笙ｪRaise me up, hold me high笙ｪ

25:01.200 --> 25:04.500
笙ｪOnly you笙ｪ

25:05.080 --> 25:08.620
笙ｪDuring the dark night笙ｪ

25:08.620 --> 25:09.380
Pay attention, guys.

25:09.380 --> 25:10.760
This is an archaic form
of the character "fa."

25:10.760 --> 25:11.330
*["Fa" means laws.]

25:11.330 --> 25:13.330
It's made up of several parts.

25:13.330 --> 25:14.290
Now look.

25:14.570 --> 25:16.770
The three dots on the left side

25:16.860 --> 25:17.900
represent water.

25:18.250 --> 25:20.250
A leveled bowl of water

25:20.250 --> 25:22.380
symbolizes fairness.

25:22.860 --> 25:24.940
As for the character on the right side,

25:25.090 --> 25:26.620
most people may not know it.

25:26.620 --> 25:28.330
It's pronounced "zhi"

25:29.010 --> 25:30.770
and means "solution."

25:30.770 --> 25:31.960
笙ｪRunning for truth笙ｪ

25:31.960 --> 25:35.620
笙ｪI find my path笙ｪ

25:35.620 --> 25:36.490
I'm off. Bye.

25:37.980 --> 25:38.570
Mom.

25:38.570 --> 25:40.620
笙ｪDrawing on the hope笙ｪ

25:40.620 --> 25:42.940
Mom found work at the school
as a cleaner.

25:43.010 --> 25:43.900
The pay is minimal,

25:44.090 --> 25:46.090
but it's enough
to cover our daily expenses.

25:46.900 --> 25:47.620
Back in high school,

25:47.620 --> 25:49.980
I cared too much
about how people saw me,

25:50.090 --> 25:51.980
and was afraid to show
the less favorable sides

25:51.980 --> 25:53.460
of my life to the public.

25:56.010 --> 25:58.980
People from all walks of life
are striving to do better here.

25:59.380 --> 26:00.250
It made me believe

26:00.250 --> 26:02.460
that my own future
was full of possibilities.

26:06.380 --> 26:08.770
I feel my will reignited,

26:08.810 --> 26:10.420
and my fighting spirit brimming.

26:10.980 --> 26:13.570
Things are looking up.

26:21.420 --> 26:22.380
By the way, Qingyu,

26:22.380 --> 26:23.770
your birthday is around the corner.

26:23.770 --> 26:26.250
I've got you a little surprise.

26:26.490 --> 26:29.380
You said you wanted
to grant Beiyu's wish, right?

26:29.380 --> 26:32.400
笙ｪBirds take a fly笙ｪ

26:32.400 --> 26:37.020
笙ｪRaise me up, hold me high笙ｪ

26:37.020 --> 26:40.320
笙ｪOnly you笙ｪ

26:40.900 --> 26:44.620
笙ｪDuring the dark night笙ｪ

26:44.620 --> 26:45.980
I used your performance clip

26:45.980 --> 26:48.290
to apply
for the Starry Cup Dance Competition.

26:48.620 --> 26:49.900
You've passed the audition.

26:49.980 --> 26:52.050
The competition
will be held in Jiangzhou.

26:52.290 --> 26:55.140
Whether or not you're going,
it's up to you.

26:55.460 --> 26:56.250
What are you reading?

26:57.700 --> 27:01.050
Notice of finalists for the 7th
Starry Cup Dance Competition.

27:02.320 --> 27:02.960
[Starry Cup Dance Competition]

27:02.960 --> 27:04.330
[Qiao Qingyu, qualified]
Wow, Qiao Qingyu.

27:04.330 --> 27:05.940
You did this without telling us.

27:06.140 --> 27:07.460
Mumu signed me up.

27:07.460 --> 27:09.050
I haven't made up my mind yet.

27:09.050 --> 27:10.460
Well, you should totally go.

27:10.860 --> 27:12.380
I remember your sister also

27:12.380 --> 27:13.770
made it into this dance competition.

27:14.010 --> 27:15.490
It's too bad she didn't take part.

27:16.090 --> 27:18.460
If she knew you were a finalist,

27:18.460 --> 27:19.940
I'm sure she'd be overjoyed.

27:20.620 --> 27:22.730
But the competition date
is just around the corner.

27:22.860 --> 27:25.050
I haven't prepared anything
in terms of choreography

27:25.050 --> 27:26.380
or outfit.

27:28.180 --> 27:30.250
Don't worry. Leave it to us.

27:41.460 --> 27:43.180
Qingyu, take a look at this version.

27:46.980 --> 27:48.530
I redesigned the bodice

27:48.530 --> 27:50.050
to accentuate your waist.

27:50.290 --> 27:51.250
As for the skirt,

27:51.250 --> 27:52.660
I think a big, loose skirt is better.

27:53.010 --> 27:54.290
Let's have some drinks.

27:54.620 --> 27:57.290
笙ｪYou opened a window笙ｪ

27:57.290 --> 27:57.900
Yours.

27:58.010 --> 27:59.180
Thanks.

27:59.620 --> 28:00.420
Thanks.

28:00.600 --> 28:04.540
笙ｪI saw hope outside the window笙ｪ

28:06.720 --> 28:10.750
笙ｪYou said something
I couldn't understand笙ｪ

28:12.540 --> 28:16.020
笙ｪAnd I realized my desire笙ｪ

28:18.680 --> 28:22.270
笙ｪYou lit up a lamp笙ｪ

28:25.240 --> 28:28.830
笙ｪI saw the light笙ｪ

28:31.080 --> 28:34.530
笙ｪYou slowly walked away笙ｪ

28:37.140 --> 28:40.780
笙ｪAnd I realized my helplessness笙ｪ

28:41.940 --> 28:43.770
Ta-da, we did it!

28:44.290 --> 28:45.090
Wow!

28:45.090 --> 28:46.550
笙ｪActually, I haven't let go笙ｪ

28:47.570 --> 28:48.860
Oh, right, Qingyu.

28:48.860 --> 28:50.180
The competition is in Jiangzhou.

28:50.180 --> 28:51.620
Will your mom let you go?

28:51.620 --> 28:53.050
笙ｪIt's just a pretense of silence笙ｪ

28:54.330 --> 28:55.730
I have an idea.

28:55.730 --> 28:58.310
笙ｪHow should I find comfort笙ｪ

28:58.790 --> 29:00.390
笙ｪIn the unknown years ahead?笙ｪ

29:01.020 --> 29:06.160
笙ｪDon't be so miserable anymore笙ｪ

29:07.970 --> 29:11.330
笙ｪI walked alone
through this heartbreaking street笙ｪ

29:11.330 --> 29:12.140
What do you think?

29:13.260 --> 29:16.010
笙ｪHow can I forget
the sight of you turning back?笙ｪ

29:16.010 --> 29:18.490
Why do you have to go to Jiangzhou
for the seminar?

29:18.730 --> 29:21.420
I don't think Mumu ever mentioned

29:21.420 --> 29:24.660
a Grade 3 recruitment seminar.

29:24.660 --> 29:26.980
It's because the school
has high hopes for Qingyu.

29:27.900 --> 29:31.180
You could rest or read on the train.

29:31.330 --> 29:33.700
Make sure not to talk to strangers.

29:35.490 --> 29:37.900
Take the chili sauce.

29:40.620 --> 29:41.420
Qingyu.

29:42.700 --> 29:44.900
I noticed you've been sneezing.

29:45.050 --> 29:46.420
Take this flu medicine with you.

29:46.420 --> 29:48.140
It's cold over there after all.

29:48.140 --> 29:48.770
Okay.

29:50.620 --> 29:51.770
Gosh, Dad.

29:52.090 --> 29:53.730
Qingyu will only be gone for two days.

29:54.050 --> 29:56.050
You can get everything in Jiangzhou.

29:56.050 --> 29:57.620
Relax, you two.

30:00.270 --> 30:02.760
[Qiao Qingyu, qualified
for the Starry Cup Dance Competition]

30:39.940 --> 30:42.050
Be good and listen to your teacher.

30:42.490 --> 30:44.330
If you're going out
for a meal or anything,

30:44.330 --> 30:45.900
go with your friends.

30:45.940 --> 30:48.090
Don't be going around by yourself, okay?

30:49.140 --> 30:51.700
I heard Jiangzhou University
is a prestigious one.

30:52.050 --> 30:53.900
Check the admission criteria
with your teacher.

30:53.980 --> 30:56.330
If possible, you should apply.

30:56.980 --> 30:58.530
Sure. I'll be off, then.

30:59.420 --> 31:00.530
Take care.

31:00.530 --> 31:01.770
Keep the money safe.

31:02.730 --> 31:05.700
Don't worry about pinching pennies
while you're gone.

31:05.700 --> 31:07.180
Spend when you need to.

31:07.380 --> 31:08.980
Grab some drinks for your classmates.

31:08.980 --> 31:10.530
It's good for networking.

31:11.380 --> 31:12.860
Mister, here's the fare.

31:12.860 --> 31:13.420
Got it.

31:13.420 --> 31:13.660
I'm off.

31:13.660 --> 31:14.010
Qingyu!

31:16.010 --> 31:16.490
Take this.

31:16.490 --> 31:17.090
What is it?

31:17.090 --> 31:18.290
Something good.
Check it out when you're on the road.

31:18.290 --> 31:19.980
Hey, take care of Mom.

31:20.770 --> 31:22.050
Don't worry.

31:22.180 --> 31:23.900
Go, or you'll miss the train.

32:15.900 --> 32:17.700
Why keep this unlucky stuff?

32:18.420 --> 32:20.660
Those were her last pair of shoes.

32:21.250 --> 32:22.660
Her belongings.

32:25.420 --> 32:28.050
Qiao Qingyu,
the qualification notice you hid

32:28.090 --> 32:29.700
almost got found by Mom.

32:30.330 --> 32:31.530
Dad saw it

32:31.770 --> 32:33.050
and said nothing.

32:34.140 --> 32:36.180
I also got Qiao Beiyu's dancing shoes

32:36.220 --> 32:37.570
a while back.

32:38.220 --> 32:39.010
You can have them.

32:39.330 --> 32:40.810
Don't lose them again.

32:46.610 --> 32:51.280
[Jiangzhou]

32:59.250 --> 33:00.380
I don't see you.

33:01.010 --> 33:02.140
I'm at the entrance.

33:02.420 --> 33:03.530
I'm coming out.

33:04.900 --> 33:06.010
I'm here!

33:08.120 --> 33:12.360
[The 7th Youth Starry Cup
Dance Competition]

33:16.380 --> 33:17.730
You already finished it?

33:17.810 --> 33:18.730
It was too good.

33:21.490 --> 33:22.570
Gosh, you have no idea.

33:22.570 --> 33:24.140
When I went to take the crayfish,

33:24.290 --> 33:26.050
those ladies were staring at me.

33:26.050 --> 33:27.660
I was about to break out in sweat.

33:28.220 --> 33:29.860
Haven't felt so embarrassed in a while.

33:30.330 --> 33:32.980
Well, I've been craving for these
for a year.

33:34.570 --> 33:35.620
You should try this.

33:35.620 --> 33:36.250
Huh?

33:36.530 --> 33:38.220
This is really nutritious

33:38.420 --> 33:39.810
and appetizing.

33:39.810 --> 33:40.860
After you drink it,

33:40.860 --> 33:42.460
you'll probably eat
two more plates full.

33:42.700 --> 33:43.810
Thanks a lot.

33:44.530 --> 33:45.090
Here.

33:46.220 --> 33:47.530
Just let me eat as I please.

33:47.530 --> 33:49.090
I can't get this overseas, you know?

33:49.090 --> 33:50.330
Go on, finish this plate.

33:50.330 --> 33:51.090
I'll get you some more.

33:51.090 --> 33:51.860
Okay, sure.

33:56.050 --> 33:57.250
What's going on with you?

33:57.460 --> 33:59.140
I can't believe

34:00.660 --> 34:01.810
you actually asked me out.

34:02.250 --> 34:03.570
Back then, when I came back,

34:03.570 --> 34:05.460
I'd be the one asking you out.

34:07.530 --> 34:09.810
It's because I've missed you.

34:10.420 --> 34:11.219
As if.

34:14.530 --> 34:18.290
I heard the girl
in the Starry Cup amateur group

34:18.290 --> 34:20.139
is from Huanzhou High School too.

34:20.420 --> 34:21.489
What was her name again?

34:22.900 --> 34:24.530
Qiao Qingyu, right?

34:25.770 --> 34:26.219
We're not friends.

34:26.219 --> 34:27.380
But you know her.

34:29.659 --> 34:30.460
By the way,

34:31.380 --> 34:33.139
my dad is in a relationship.

34:33.810 --> 34:34.860
That's normal.

34:36.010 --> 34:36.940
I also heard

34:37.570 --> 34:39.570
that you were their matchmaker.

34:40.380 --> 34:41.980
I was trying to divert the attention.

34:42.219 --> 34:43.139
This will save me

34:43.139 --> 34:45.620
from his constant supervision.
It's annoying.

34:52.810 --> 34:56.570
There's something important
I wanted to talk to you about

34:57.380 --> 34:58.490
today.

35:00.090 --> 35:00.900
What is it?

35:02.700 --> 35:05.420
Chengyu has been

35:09.250 --> 35:10.420
asking me to marry him.

35:11.900 --> 35:13.290
Don't stare at me like that.

35:17.380 --> 35:18.730
I wanted to hear from you

35:20.140 --> 35:21.660
before I answered.

35:26.700 --> 35:30.860
What are your true feelings

35:32.090 --> 35:33.780
about him?

35:33.780 --> 35:35.050
What a serious question.

35:36.340 --> 35:37.530
Let me think.

35:40.940 --> 35:43.090
You know, he is

35:43.940 --> 35:46.420
the kind of person
who is free-spirited and open-minded.

35:47.650 --> 35:48.900
A simple guy.

35:49.210 --> 35:51.050
No matter what it is,

35:51.570 --> 35:52.610
it's either yes or no.

35:52.610 --> 35:54.010
He never over-thinks like I do.

35:55.570 --> 35:57.780
One thing stood out to me though.

35:58.460 --> 35:59.530
He told me

36:00.210 --> 36:03.340
that you've been chasing after success.

36:04.460 --> 36:05.940
Actually, success is simply

36:06.460 --> 36:08.460
a natural outcome of hard work

36:08.460 --> 36:10.170
applied to talent.

36:10.170 --> 36:11.420
There's no need to pursue it.

36:11.860 --> 36:12.820
Compared to success,

36:13.610 --> 36:15.050
a happy, healthy life

36:15.570 --> 36:17.050
is more important.

36:17.530 --> 36:18.340
I think

36:18.340 --> 36:19.980
his lifestyle and values

36:19.980 --> 36:22.340
are unconsciously affecting me.

36:23.570 --> 36:24.530
He's the kind

36:24.570 --> 36:27.010
to get anxious
or lose sleep over things.

36:27.460 --> 36:28.300
Unlike me.

36:29.610 --> 36:31.380
I'm a perfectionist

36:32.570 --> 36:34.050
and always afraid of making mistakes.

36:36.820 --> 36:38.050
Personality-wise,

36:39.740 --> 36:41.050
or should I say mentally,

36:42.900 --> 36:44.530
we complement one another.

36:44.940 --> 36:47.210
But there's one thing
that's been holding me back.

36:47.940 --> 36:48.740
You know it.

36:50.860 --> 36:52.650
I haven't been able to move on from it.

37:02.420 --> 37:03.170
Mom.

37:04.130 --> 37:04.940
Although

37:06.130 --> 37:07.780
I'm unable to give you
any useful suggestions,

37:09.260 --> 37:11.900
I still wish you happiness.

37:16.380 --> 37:17.460
That's quite sudden.

37:24.900 --> 37:25.690
Thank you.

37:33.210 --> 37:34.260
I'm so tired.

37:34.260 --> 37:35.490
Let's get some rest.

37:35.490 --> 37:36.130
Hmm.

37:37.170 --> 37:39.210
Hey, miss. Is there anyone inside?

37:39.210 --> 37:40.260
I don't think so.

37:40.260 --> 37:41.210
Thanks.

37:55.050 --> 37:56.570
Their food was pretty good.

37:57.460 --> 37:59.380
I can't believe
the amount of crayfish you ate though.

38:00.690 --> 38:01.380
[Registration]
Ms. Anna.

38:01.860 --> 38:02.860
This is your work pass.

38:02.860 --> 38:03.420
Oh, thanks.

38:03.420 --> 38:04.900
The competition will start
at 8 AM tomorrow.

38:04.900 --> 38:05.610
Got it.

38:05.650 --> 38:07.210
Sir, we're still unable to get through.

38:07.530 --> 38:08.380
What's the matter?

38:08.690 --> 38:09.490
Here's the thing.

38:09.490 --> 38:11.050
The hotel notified us
that they had overbooked the rooms.

38:11.050 --> 38:12.980
One of the amateur group participants
hasn't turned up,

38:12.980 --> 38:14.260
nor did she leave any contact details.

38:14.260 --> 38:14.610
So,

38:14.610 --> 38:16.090
we weren't able to save a room for her.

38:16.460 --> 38:17.090
Oh.

38:17.690 --> 38:18.490
Who is it?

38:20.940 --> 38:21.860
Qiao Qingyu?

38:23.170 --> 38:25.050
This afternoon,
when I arrived at the hotel,

38:25.050 --> 38:26.460
I saw a few girls

38:26.460 --> 38:27.780
heading straight to the practice hall.

38:28.050 --> 38:29.340
Maybe she's there.

38:29.340 --> 38:30.570
You could try looking for her there.

38:32.090 --> 38:33.980
Mom, can I have this?

38:34.380 --> 38:35.260
Where are you going?

38:46.260 --> 38:47.530
Hey, what are you doing?

38:47.570 --> 38:48.260
I'm looking for someone.

38:48.260 --> 38:48.820
We're closed.

38:48.820 --> 38:49.860
I'm looking for someone!

38:50.630 --> 38:56.310
笙ｪThe more we care,
the more careful we become笙ｪ

38:57.410 --> 39:02.810
笙ｪCounting the distance that separates us笙ｪ

39:03.630 --> 39:09.410
笙ｪA single step, and we'd be closer still笙ｪ

39:11.490 --> 39:13.050
There is someone here.

39:13.340 --> 39:15.170
Miss, why were you so careless?

39:15.170 --> 39:17.070
笙ｪTurns out that what's on my mind笙ｪ

39:17.920 --> 39:21.590
笙ｪIs your name笙ｪ

39:22.070 --> 39:27.290
笙ｪThe only stubbornness in my heart笙ｪ

39:27.990 --> 39:31.420
笙ｪAt first sight笙ｪ

39:31.990 --> 39:35.140
笙ｪThe future has been determined笙ｪ

39:35.920 --> 39:38.210
笙ｪDreams began to feel real笙ｪ

39:38.210 --> 39:41.130
My mom is the guest judge
for this year's Starry Cup.

39:41.340 --> 39:42.130
I asked her,

39:42.340 --> 39:44.210
and she said your room was canceled

39:44.260 --> 39:46.340
because you missed
the registration deadline.

39:46.860 --> 39:48.900
The hotel is full,

39:49.090 --> 39:50.050
but if you don't mind,

39:50.490 --> 39:51.570
you can stay

39:52.010 --> 39:53.530
in my room tonight.

39:53.530 --> 39:56.580
笙ｪWhere the same story is held dear笙ｪ

39:57.170 --> 39:59.490
As usual, you can have the bed.

39:59.690 --> 40:00.690
I'll sleep on the sofa.

40:01.150 --> 40:04.340
笙ｪCourage wasn't late too笙ｪ

40:04.910 --> 40:11.040
笙ｪOnly then does time
not betray our acquaintance笙ｪ

40:36.460 --> 40:37.610
If you don't dry your hair,

40:37.940 --> 40:39.170
you might get sick tomorrow.

41:05.650 --> 41:06.690
What's on your mind?

41:10.460 --> 41:11.460
Well...

41:13.460 --> 41:15.130
You seem to be always there
whenever I need help.

41:20.260 --> 41:20.980
Are you feeling touched?

41:23.530 --> 41:24.980
I don't want to owe you anything.

41:36.570 --> 41:37.490
I expect

41:38.650 --> 41:39.900
the favor to be repaid.

41:40.780 --> 41:41.690
But not right now.

42:18.280 --> 42:21.970
笙ｪPerhaps笙ｪ

42:22.480 --> 42:28.180
笙ｪThe more we care,
the more careful we become笙ｪ

42:29.320 --> 42:34.720
笙ｪCounting the distance
that separates us笙ｪ

42:35.720 --> 42:41.280
笙ｪA single step,
and we'd be closer still笙ｪ

42:46.950 --> 42:50.620
笙ｪIn the future笙ｪ

42:51.080 --> 42:56.800
笙ｪTime will reveal this secret笙ｪ

42:58.300 --> 43:03.370
笙ｪWaiting is a silent promise笙ｪ

43:04.620 --> 43:09.780
笙ｪThat never expires笙ｪ

43:13.380 --> 43:17.850
笙ｪTurns out that what's on my mind笙ｪ

43:18.850 --> 43:22.520
笙ｪIs your name笙ｪ

43:23.020 --> 43:28.120
笙ｪThe only stubbornness in my heart笙ｪ

43:29.200 --> 43:32.420
笙ｪAt first sight笙ｪ

43:32.850 --> 43:36.130
笙ｪThe future has been determined笙ｪ

43:36.820 --> 43:42.380
笙ｪDreams began to feel real笙ｪ

43:43.480 --> 43:47.020
笙ｪTurns out that what's on your mind笙ｪ

43:47.480 --> 43:51.420
笙ｪIs a place笙ｪ

43:51.720 --> 43:57.280
笙ｪWhere the same story is held dear笙ｪ

43:57.950 --> 44:01.320
笙ｪFortunately, I'm not sensible enough笙ｪ

44:01.650 --> 44:05.120
笙ｪCourage wasn't late too笙ｪ

44:05.650 --> 44:11.720
笙ｪOnly then does time not betray
our acquaintance笙ｪ
